long_description: ecotyl is a lifestyle brand that aims to elevate health and wellness in the most sustainable way possible. we firmly believe that the food we consume and the products we use daily leave a long-lasting impression on our health and the environment. we're redefining your life experience and believe in the power of fresh, natural and organic ingredients that are carefully sourced. what sets us apart is our unwavering commitment to consistent innovation, creating products that are not just flavourful but also highly functional to elevate your lifestyles in a convenient and sustainable way. our product range of over 50 products is organized into six categories: superfoods, ethical beauty, beverages, eco-conscious lifestyles, daily essentials, and personal care. all our offerings adhere to a vegan, pesticide-free, unadulterated, gmo-free standard, devoid of added food colors or artificial flavors.
